<br>
The other major problem is that multiple people from every guild seem to post thier guild's schedule, many times conflicting with one another. To date, scheduling have led to as much confusion as it was meant to avoid.<br>
<br>
I think Lyion, Fell and Draed are all very reasonable people, and would be willing to share with one another. But, sharing is a give and take process. Maybe we should have a seperate forum that only guild leaders (and maybe officers) have access to. This would allow the guilds to schedule planes without the peanut gallery (us), to get pissed at each other =)<br>
<br>
my two cents...<br>
<br>
